Tiles.Text: Bigfoot looks crazy and hard to believe because it leaves behind tracks.
Since there is evidence of Bigfoot, people must have taken blurry photos of Bigfoot.
Bigfoot tracks looks nowhere near as crazy as sharks.
There are some blurry photos of Bigfoot.
Sharks look really crazy and hard to believe.
Blurry photos are hard to make out, so Bigfoot looks crazy and hard to believe.
All photos of Bigfoot are blurry, so Bigfoot must be blurry.
It isn't crazy for Bigfoot to exist and there is evidence, therefore, Bigfoot exists.
If sharks look crazy but they exist, then Bigfoot isn't too crazy to exist.
If there are Bigfoot tracks, then there is evidence of Bigfoot.
Bigfoot looks crazy and hard to believe.
I saw Bigfoot tracks one time.
